</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="354B36B45650FFE5D1B7F9ADFEA663B6" blockId="76.[108,636,1614,1737]" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">
VOUCHER MATERIAL (TOTAL = 6): 
<collectingCountry id="4DE376245650FFE5D338F9ACFD9F6319" box="[515,552,1614,1638]" name="Iceland" pageId="76" pageNumber="76">Isla</collectingCountry>
